name: "Diamond Hands" (Standard Edition)
description:
"Diamond Hands", a Wolfe+Castle production (Mr. Wildenfree & AG DYNASTY), is the second track from the upcoming album, "Still Flowing". This standard edition NFT is coupled with an animated cover art, created with machine learning/generative art & my own human selection.

Copyright is not transferred with ownership of this NFT. As a collector of this piece, you are free to share, play, & showcase this music art in all non-commercial settings or as part of a DJ set. Naturally, you are also free to resell on the secondary market. Ownership of this standard edition NFT does not provide the collector with rights to streaming royalties, but will cement you as an early patron of Mr. Wildenfree & ownership of a piece of this legacy in the making.

Word in the meteverse is... those who hold a Wildenfree NFT this early may find themselves in a better position for future releases.

Welll...
